ance do Shanghai Fudan Institute of Visual Arts.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yan Feng","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yan Feng","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Янь Фэн","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"严丰","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"嚴豐","primary":false}}]}},"person_1524100_translations":{"at":1773689216535,"data":{"id":1524100,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Tom Keir Blyth (born February 2, 1995) is an English actor from Birmingham. He had his first lead role in the film Scott and Sid (2018), and has since starred as Glen Byam Shaw in Benediction (2021) and Coriolanus Snow in The Hunger Games: The Ballad of Songbirds & Snakes (2023). On television, he has played the title role in the MGM+ series Billy the Kid (2022–present).","name":"Tom Blyth","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Tom Keir Blyth (nascido em 2 de fevereiro de 1995) é um ator inglês. Seus filmes incluem Scott and Sid (2018), Benediction (2021) e Jogos Vorazes: A Cantiga dos Pássaros e das Serpentes (2023). Na televisão, ele protagonizou como o personagem-título na série da Epix, Billy the Kid (2022).","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"💥Том Эдвард Блайт. Родился в 1995-ом году в Ноттингеме, Великобритания. Рос в семье со старшей сестрой. Отец работал продюсером, а мать была учительницей. Учился в Джульярдской школе драмы. Работает актёром. Личную жизнь предпочитает держать в тайне\n\n🎬Главные проекты🎬: «Голодные игры: Баллада о змеях и певчих птицах» (2023), «Билли Кид» (2022), «Моя леди Джейн» (2024)\n\n⭐Интересный факт⭐: Том самостоятельно исполнял многие сцены с лошадьми и оружием в «Билли Кид»","name":"Том Блайт","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Tom Keir Blyth ist ein britischer Schauspieler.\n\nBlyth wurde im Februar 1995 als Sohn des Produzenten Gavin Blyth und der Berufsberaterin Charlotte in Birmingham geboren. Er wuchs mit seiner Schwester Anya in Woodthorpe, einem Vorort von Nottingham, auf. Nach dem Besuch der Arnold Hill Academy und des Bilborough College absolvierte er 2020 seinen Abschluss an der Juilliard School in New York City.\n\nBlyth begann seine Schauspielkarriere 2010 als Kinderdarsteller in den Filmen Robin Hood und Pelican Blood. 2018 spielte Blyth an der Seite von Richard Mason in dem Coming-of-Age-Film Scott and Sid mit. In dem 2021 veröffentlichten Kriegsdrama Benediction übernahm er die Rolle des Glen Byam Shaw. 2022 hatte er eine Gastrolle in der HBO-Fernsehserie The Gilded Age.\n\nSeit April 2022 verkörpert Blyth die Rolle des William H. Bonney in der Epix-Fernsehserie Billy the Kid.\n\nBlyth wurde im Mai 2022 für die Rolle des Coriolanus Snow in der Verfilmung des Romanes Die Tribute von Panem X – Das Lied von Vogel und Schlange von Suzanne Collins auserwählt.[3] Er trat somit im November 2023 in die Fußstapfen von Donald Sutherland, der die Rolle in den vorherigen Filmen verkörperte. (Quelle: Wikipedia)","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"汤姆·布莱斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Том Блайт","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"湯姆·布萊斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"톰 블라이스","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"湯姆·布萊斯","primary":false}}]}},"person_5352534_translations":{"at":1773689217773,"data":{"id":5352534,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yang Yunying","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"杨云英","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"楊雲英","primary":false}}]}},"person_1916848_translations":{"at":1773689219183,"data":{"id":1916848,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Kate Trefry is a screenwriter, director, and graduate of NYU. Her feature scripts PURE O and REVOLVER both made their respective year’s annual Black List for Hollywood’s best-unproduced screenplays, the latter having Chernin producing with Andrew Stanton (WALL-E) attached to direct. She currently writes on the Netflix series STRANGER THINGS, and loves animals and babies, despite the content of this short. HOW TO BE ALONE is her directorial debut.","name":"Kate Trefry","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"Кейт Трефри — сценарист, режиссёр и выпускница Нью-Йоркского университета. Её сценарии к полнометражным фильмам «Чистота» и «Револьвер» вошли в ежегодный чёрный список лучших нереализованных сценариев Голливуда. Продюсером последнего выступил Чернин, а режиссёром — Эндрю Стэнтон («ВАЛЛ-И»). В настоящее время она пишет сценарии для сериала Netflix «Очень странные дела» и любит животных и детей, несмотря на содержание этой короткометражки. «Как быть одному» — её режиссёрский дебют.","name":"Кейт Трефри","primary":false}}]}},"person_5765543_translations":{"at":1773689220215,"data":{"id":5765543,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Martin Zannato","primary":true}}]}}}}